                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        




<div class="warning-box">
<div class="warning-img"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-3306/warning2.png" alt="warning2.png" class="image" /><br /></div>
<div class="warning-text">
<p><span style="font-size:105%;"><span style="color: firebrick"><strong>本文档已因超时空数据污染而被标记</strong>。</span></span><br />
若你遭遇任何技术性障碍，请在六十秒后重新载入页面。<br />
